Package: scMultiome
Type: Package
Title: Toolkit for Integrating and Visualizing Multi-Omics Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Giovanni", "Gavatorta",
      email = "giovanni.gavatorta@edu.unito.it",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Imports:
    GenomicRanges,
    IRanges,
    rtracklayer,
    data.table,
    ggplot2,
    dplyr
Description: Provides functions for integrating, normalizing, and visualizing multi-omics datasets,
 including gene expression and ATAC-seq data. The package features genomic annotation,
 overlap analysis of genomic ranges, and interactive plots organized by chromosome.
